name: Car Availability
query:
select 
v.name as 'Car:Data:300',
case IFNULL(sit.name,0)
WHEN 0 THEN 'Available'
ELSE 'BOOKED' END AS 'Status:Data:100'
from `tabVehicle` AS v
LEFT JOIN `tabSales Invoice Item` as sit 
ON v.name = sit.vehicle_cf
AND sit.parent in (select name from `tabSales Invoice` where posting_date = %(as_on_date)s)
